<h3>Tools Used</h3>

<ul>
<li>Power BI</li>
<li>DAX</li>
<li>Power Query</li>
<li>Excel</li>
</ul>

<h3>KPIs</h3>

<ul>
<li>Total Runs</li>
<li>Total Wickets</li>
<li>Average Strike Rate</li>
<li>Top Run Scorer</li>
<li>Top Wicket Taker</li>
</ul>

